# Copy this file to .env and fill in your own keys for local development.
# .env is gitignored and will never be committed or deployed.
#
# Note: this app does NOT read these at runtime — the deployed site asks each
# visitor to paste their own key into the sidebar on the valuation tool page.
# These vars are only here if you want to wire up a local-only convenience
# (e.g. auto-filling the sidebar in dev mode). Do not use them in any code
# path that runs in the production build — Vite inlines VITE_* vars into the
# public JS bundle at build time, and `npm run deploy` publishes that bundle
# to GitHub Pages for anyone to read. Baking a real key into that bundle
# exposes it to every visitor, same as committing it.

VITE_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
VITE_FMP_API_KEY=
